{"tid":1610353,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"賀中國70年國慶 特朗普：美國終將獲勝","createTime":"2019-10-01T17:10:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T00:42:12.000Z","uid":141151,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1d130559e8587caafeb093c4934154c557812a96","tid":1610353,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:10:47.000Z","msg":"賀中國70年國慶 特朗普：美國終將獲勝<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20190930-%E8%B3%80%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B70%E5%B9%B4%E5%9C%8B%E6%85%B6-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%B5%82%E5%B0%87%E7%8D%B2%E5%8B%9D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20190930-%25E8%25B3%2580%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B70%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2585%25B6-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25B5%2582%25E5%25B0%2587%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%258B%259D&d=0svHhEbJ%2FFd80Myex1SsDfkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=35c38de8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20190930-%E8%B3%80%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B70%E5%B9%B4%E5%9C%8B%E6%85%B6-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%B5%82%E5%B0%87%E7%8D%B2%E5%8B%9D</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>中央社消息，美國總統特朗普9月30日發出一連串推文，除祝賀中國國慶70周年，也表示華盛頓已意識到中國企圖超越美國的野心，並表示在他的帶領下，美國終將贏得最後勝利。</strong><br />\n<br />\n特朗普在推特談到中國貿易陷入混亂時說，&ldquo;中國力促一個冷靜、理性的解決辦法&rdquo;，&ldquo;中國表現非常糟糕，然而美國在你們最喜愛的總統領導下，（經濟表現）持續屢創新高，就算民主黨人什麼都沒做，我們正開始而已&rdquo;！<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n特朗普另提到：多年後，美國終於意識到，北京超越我們成為21世紀經濟與軍事超級強權的計畫及雄心。現在發生的就是，美國總算加以回應（謝謝你特朗普總統）。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n十一國慶前一天，美國總統特朗普在推文中還表示，&ldquo;這發生在貿易，這正在軍事競爭中形塑，&hellip;，我們正贏得勝利，我們將會獲勝，他們不該毀壞我們和他們的協議。生日快樂，中國！&rdquo;"},{"pid":"3ceb1b721a097bcccaf9e775b63460a03226aff6","tid":1610353,"uid":220701,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:11:53.000Z","msg":"生日快樂，中國<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">生日快樂，中國</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">生日快樂，中國</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26eb196b640c703b51ed4ffb2802d79e823084cc","tid":1610353,"uid":74155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:14:06.000Z","msg":"香港人都有送大禮過支共㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faee6cf2f0f165e03d58c66467e3cc3b6ea6915f","tid":1610353,"uid":120431,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:17:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3a92c69b7f96135f88988c37d86c9d1260d8484","tid":1610353,"uid":228955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:17:51.000Z","msg":"好正一定要記錄低十一 暴動"},{"pid":"b312caa3c19c4451b73398332e773a28eb7be860","tid":1610353,"uid":153239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ceb1b721a097bcccaf9e775b63460a03226aff6","tid":1610353,"uid":220701,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:11:53.000Z","msg":"生日快樂，中國<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">生日快樂，中國</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">生日快樂，中國</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:19:25.000Z","msg":"送大禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b08b908bfd5c4f27cefa5cc9b0b7ca3f152ec40f","tid":1610353,"uid":322732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:19:30.000Z","msg":"收野喇 雜大大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ab434aa10811288a835ad7d0acc21d03d84c5e","tid":1610353,"uid":30900,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:19:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">SIR THIS WAY </span></strong>"},{"pid":